<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type"/>
</head>
<body>
<div>
  <% if @local_language == "en" %>
      <p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>

      <p>This following advertiser approval by mail failed, probably because it had already been approved or incorrect
        mail reply. </p>

      <p>Advertiser  <%= @client.code %>: <%= @client.clientname %> |
        Brand: <%= @client.brand? ? @client.brand : "-" %> |
        Agency: <%= @client.channel_name %> </p>

      <p>Link: http://<%= CURRENT_DOMAIN %>/en/clients/<%= @client.id %></p>

      <p>Please login to the system for details.</p>

      <% if @body %>
          E-mail Reply:
          <%= @body %>
      <% end %>

      <p>If any enquiries, please contact: technology@i-click.com </p>

      <p>Regards,</p>

      <p>iClick Interactive Asia Limited </p>

  <% else %>
      <p>您好: </p>

      <p>以下广告主通过邮件审批失败，原因可能是已被审批 或 回复不正确。</p>

      <p>广告主 <%= @client.code %>: <%= @client.clientname %> | 品牌: <%= @client.brand? ? @client.brand : "-" %> |
        代理公司: <%=  @client.channel_name  %> </p>

      <p>链接：http://<%= CURRENT_DOMAIN %>/zh-cn/clients/<%= @client.id %> </p>

      <p>您可以登录系统查看详情。</p>
      <% if @body %>
          邮件回复内容：
          <%= @body %>
      <% end %>
      <p>如有问题，请联系: technology@i-click.com </p>

      <p>谢谢</p>

      <p>爱点击互动（北京）广告有限公司 </p>
  <% end %>
</div>
</body>
</html>